    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; residual risk is bounded by the Medium model influence classification and the satisfactory outcome of all three quantitative QoI comparisons (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is accepted as sufficiently credible for the intended regulatory decision context.",
